If ROLE == Strike:
    Track primary target
    If target locked by ABM:
        Execute evasive maneuver set
    Detonate upon proximity or impact

If ROLE == Decoy:
    Match heat & radar profile of Strike
    Draw enemy interceptor lock-on
    Self-destruct after max range

If ROLE == EW:
    Emit jamming burst
    Scramble radar bands dynamically
    Tail Alpha or Relay Node to protect signal

If ROLE == Alpha:
    Maintain swarm-wide state
    Issue reassignments on node loss
    Periodically pulse nav correction
